    "body" : "<pre><code>when(\n  fooDao.getBar(\n    any(Bazoo.class)\n  )\n).thenReturn(myFoo);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>or (to avoid <code>null</code>s):</p>\n\n<pre><code>when(\n  fooDao.getBar(\n    (Bazoo)notNull()\n  )\n).thenReturn(myFoo);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Don't forget to import matchers (many others are available):</p>\n\n<p>For Mockito 2.1.0 and newer: </p>\n\n<pre><code>import static org.mockito.ArgumentMatchers.*;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>For older versions: </p>\n\n<pre><code>import static org.mockito.Matchers.*;\n</code></pre>\n"
